Package: Trex
Title: Methods for dual TCR and expression single-cell embedding 
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Nick", family = "Borcherding", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ncborch@gmail.com"), 
person(given = "Drew", family = "Voigt", role = c("aut"), email = "drewvoigt@gmail.com")
)
Description: Implementation of the Trex algorithm for single cell embedding based on TCR sequences. Package includes standalone function to calculate multilayered network from a variety of TCR metrics and interaction with SingleCellExperiment or Seurat data objects. 

